Flaherty Says He’s Optimistic About U.S.-Canada Tax Dispute

-- B y   C h a r l e s   M e a d
-- 
2011-10-05T14:00:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/flaherty-says-he-s-optimistic-about-u-s-canada-tax-dispute.html
Canadian Finance Minister  Jim
Flaherty  said he’s optimistic there will be a resolution in a
tax dispute with the  Internal Revenue Service  that involves U.S.
citizens living in  Canada .  Flaherty made the comments to reporters in  New York .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Charles Mead in New York at 
